import React from 'react'
import {Nav} from 'react-bootstrap'

function ProductTable() {
    return (
        <Nav fill variant="tabs" defaultActiveKey="/home">
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link href="/home">Dashboard</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link href="/Shop">Shop</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="">Product Analysis</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="">Sales Marketing</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="">Financial Management</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="">Reports</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="">Configurations</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        </Nav>
    )
}

export default ProductTable
